                    "name": "Chinese Level 5 11 Y1",
                    "track": "school",
                    "description": "This course is designed for high school students who had already finished 800 hours of non-native Chinese language course. This course aims to train students to understand and use complicated grammars. Students are required to memorize over 2000 new words and able to use more than 100 grammar regulations in a precise way. In the meanwhile, they will be familiar with topics of modern Chinese society and traditional culture in this course. They are expected to be able to write essays of over 300 words in this course.",
