                {   "id": "ART109E100",
                    "name": "Arts 9",
                    "track": "school",
                    "level": "S",
                    "description": "Through this course, the students will learn different types of art such as woodcut printing, advanced watercolor, advanced sketching, Chinese Gongbi painting, Chinese freehand painting, oil painting, computer design. This course will help students further explore each types of art.",
