                    "track": "school",
                    "level": "S",
                    "description": "This course provides students with opportunities to continue the development of their art-making skills in order to express their own ideas, thoughts, and feelings through not just artwork and projects, but also research toward their work. There is a focus on creating artwork towards a portfolio while showing an understanding of the elements of art, principles of design, composition development, and an overview of the historical aspects of art. Students will be assessed on the research they keep in a sketchbook, art projects, class discussions and critiques, and tests that consist of vocabulary and critical thinking.",
