                    "description": "This course is designed to teach students general Physics concepts. The course of this year focuses on the concepts and laws of modern physics such as rotation, thermal physics, and electromagnetism. The topics are studied in general. Students are required to spend 6 to 10 hours on practical work, including one project each 16understanding of Physics.",
